## 고차 함수 (Higher-order Functions)

### 개념

**함수를 입력받거나 반환하는 함수**입니다.

### 함수형 유틸리티

#### 1. 함수 합성 (Composition)

```rust
pub fn compose(
    f: Box<dyn Fn(i64) -> i64>,
    g: Box<dyn Fn(i64) -> i64>,
) -> Box<dyn Fn(i64) -> i64> {
    Box::new(move |x| f(g(x)))  // (f ∘ g)(x) = f(g(x))
}

// 사용
let double = |x| x * 2;
let inc = |x| x + 1;
let composed = compose(
    Box::new(inc),
    Box::new(double),
);
composed(5);  // inc(double(5)) = inc(10) = 11
```

#### 2. 부분 적용 (Partial Application)

```rust
pub fn partial_apply(
    func: &GogsFunction,
    bound_args: Vec<i64>,
) -> Result<GogsFunction, String> {
    // 일부 인자를 미리 바인딩
    Ok(GogsFunction::new(
        func.parameters[bound_args.len()..].to_vec(),
        Box::new(move |_env, args| {
            let mut all_args = bound_args.clone();
            all_args.extend_from_slice(args);
            Ok(all_args.iter().sum())
        }),
    ))
}

// 사용
let add = GogsFunction::new(vec!["x", "y"], ...);
let add_5 = partial_apply(&add, vec![5])?;
add_5.call(&[10])?;  // 15
```

#### 3. 맵 (Map)

```rust
pub fn map_with_function(
    values: Vec<i64>,
    transformer: &GogsFunction,
) -> Result<Vec<i64>, String> {
    let mut result = Vec::new();
    for value in values {
        let transformed = transformer.call(&[value])?;
        result.push(transformed);
    }
    Ok(result)
}

// 사용
let double = GogsFunction::new(vec!["x"], ...);
map_with_function(vec![1, 2, 3], &double)?;  // [2, 4, 6]
```

#### 4. 필터 (Filter)

```rust
pub fn filter_with_function(
    values: Vec<i64>,
    predicate: &GogsFunction,
) -> Result<Vec<i64>, String> {
    let mut result = Vec::new();
    for value in values {
        let is_match = predicate.call(&[value])?;
        if is_match != 0 {
            result.push(value);
        }
    }
    Ok(result)
}

// 사용
let is_even = GogsFunction::new(vec!["x"], ...);
filter_with_function(vec![1, 2, 3, 4], &is_even)?;  // [2, 4]
```

#### 5. 축약 (Fold)

```rust
pub fn fold_with_function(
    values: Vec<i64>,
    initial: i64,
    combiner: &GogsFunction,
) -> Result<i64, String> {
    let mut accumulator = initial;
    for value in values {
        accumulator = combiner.call(&[accumulator, value])?;
    }
    Ok(accumulator)
}

// 사용
let add = GogsFunction::new(vec!["a", "b"], ...);
fold_with_function(vec![1, 2, 3], 0, &add)?;  // 6
```

